repos/dali-ui/wiki/ImageView.md:486:- **Asynchronous loading by default.** Use `ResourceReadySignal()` to know when loading completes.
repos/dali-ui/wiki/ImageView.md:489:- **Memory management.** Use `ReleasePolicy` to control when textures are released. `NEVER` should be used carefully as it can lead to memory leaks.
